<% if true # @package.shipping_estimate %>
  The shipper is ready to send the package to you! First, please pay the required shipping fees.<br />
  The total cost of the shipment comes to: <strong>$<%= '12.34' || @package.shipping_estimate %></strong>.

  <div class="buttons">
    <button class="btn btn-primary">Pay with Stripe</button>
  </div>
<% else %>
  The shipper has received the package! We will notify you when it is ready to be shipped to you.
<% end %>
